00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

1
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:42,060
=Twin Fire Dawn=

2
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:45,060
=Episode 6=

3
00:00:48,740 --> 00:00:49,820
You...

4
00:00:55,220 --> 00:00:56,940
Zhuang Yunqiu...

5
00:01:01,740 --> 00:01:02,780
(Lily?)

6
00:01:03,220 --> 00:01:04,700
(I thought she was dead.)

7
00:01:05,100 --> 00:01:07,340
(She was the one
who sided with Gu Nianchi back then)

8
00:01:07,540 --> 00:01:08,940
(and betrayed our family.)

9
00:01:09,140 --> 00:01:10,580
Weren't you dead?

10
00:01:11,460 --> 00:01:12,580
Yunqiu?

11
00:01:13,900 --> 00:01:14,539
That's right.

12
00:01:14,540 --> 00:01:15,380
Commander,

13
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:16,700
don't you recognize her?

14
00:01:16,800 --> 00:01:18,850
She's Zhuang Yunqiu,
the daughter of the Zhuang family.

15
00:01:18,850 --> 00:01:21,712
The Zhuang family smuggled opium,
and you executed them according to the law.

16
00:01:21,860 --> 00:01:23,260
You're the one who escaped.

17
00:01:23,460 --> 00:01:25,340
You must be here
to take revenge on Commander.

18
00:01:25,460 --> 00:01:26,260
Commander,

19
00:01:26,660 --> 00:01:27,980
you have to kill her.

20
00:01:29,260 --> 00:01:30,180
This...

21
00:01:30,220 --> 00:01:31,580
Miss Lily?

22
00:01:32,060 --> 00:01:34,899
I'm the Commander's lawful wife,
married into the family with full ceremony.

23
00:01:34,900 --> 00:01:35,740
My name is Xue Wan.

24
00:01:35,860 --> 00:01:37,260
The way you're acting now,

25
00:01:38,060 --> 00:01:40,020
are you not taking me seriously at all?

26
00:01:40,260 --> 00:01:41,500
Xue Wan?

27
00:01:42,100 --> 00:01:43,219
Zhuang Yunqiu,

28
00:01:43,220 --> 00:01:44,300
stop pretending.

29
00:01:44,420 --> 00:01:45,499
I grew up with you.

30
00:01:45,500 --> 00:01:46,820
There's no way I'd mistake you.

31
00:01:49,900 --> 00:01:50,700
Commander,

32
00:01:51,140 --> 00:01:53,219
she must've taken Xue Wan's identity

33
00:01:53,220 --> 00:01:54,179
to come back for revenge.

34
00:01:54,180 --> 00:01:55,360
Have you caused enough trouble?

35
00:01:55,620 --> 00:01:56,740
If you keep this up,

36
00:01:56,860 --> 00:01:58,220
I'll have someone drag you out.

37
00:01:58,540 --> 00:01:59,380
Commander,

38
00:01:59,860 --> 00:02:01,100
I'm telling the truth.

39
00:02:01,100 --> 00:02:03,300
I've been by your side for years.
Don't you know me by now?

40
00:02:03,420 --> 00:02:05,100
She really is Zhuang Yunqiu.

41
00:02:07,740 --> 00:02:08,900
I remember now.

42
00:02:09,700 --> 00:02:11,540
There's a scar on her shoulder.

43
00:02:11,620 --> 00:02:12,380
Let go of me.

44
00:02:13,060 --> 00:02:14,379
You seduced him,

45
00:02:14,380 --> 00:02:15,700
and now you're trying to frame me?

46
00:02:15,740 --> 00:02:17,660
Do you really think
I'm someone you can push around?

47
00:02:17,980 --> 00:02:19,140
Frame you?

48
00:02:19,980 --> 00:02:20,860
Fine.

49
00:02:21,220 --> 00:02:23,459
Then take off your clothes
and let everyone see.

50
00:02:23,460 --> 00:02:26,860
Let's see whether
there's a scar on your shoulder.

51
00:02:33,740 --> 00:02:35,340
Whether I have a scar or not,

52
00:02:36,700 --> 00:02:37,900
he knows best.

53
00:02:38,860 --> 00:02:39,740
Commander,

54
00:02:40,700 --> 00:02:42,100
you believe me, don't you?

55
00:02:52,780 --> 00:02:55,020
No one knows whether
my wife has a scar better than I do.

56
00:02:55,540 --> 00:02:56,620
That's enough, Lily.

57
00:02:56,660 --> 00:02:57,740
Commander,

58
00:02:57,780 --> 00:02:59,340
don't let her fool you.

59
00:02:59,620 --> 00:03:01,940
I'm doing this for your own good.
She really is Zhuang Yunqiu.

60
00:03:01,940 --> 00:03:05,060
And she's no refined young lady either.

61
00:03:05,180 --> 00:03:06,059
A few winters ago,

62
00:03:06,060 --> 00:03:07,900
she ran off for days
without coming home...

63
00:03:12,340 --> 00:03:13,540
Miss Lily,

64
00:03:13,660 --> 00:03:15,859
I think I've already
shown you enough respect.

65
00:03:15,860 --> 00:03:17,060
I'd advise you

66
00:03:17,260 --> 00:03:18,900
not to push your luck any further.

67
00:03:19,220 --> 00:03:20,340
Words mean nothing.

68
00:03:20,980 --> 00:03:23,060
If you're not Zhuang Yunqiu,

69
00:03:23,380 --> 00:03:25,179
then take off your clothes
and let everyone see.

70
00:03:25,180 --> 00:03:26,460
We'll all be witnesses for you.

71
00:03:27,540 --> 00:03:28,380
What?

72
00:03:28,980 --> 00:03:29,940
Zhuang Yunqiu.

73
00:03:30,580 --> 00:03:32,220
Don't tell me you're feeling guilty

74
00:03:32,540 --> 00:03:33,660
and too afraid to do it.

75
00:03:34,580 --> 00:03:37,260
Another woman fighting
over the Commander again.

76
00:03:37,460 --> 00:03:38,620
I've heard about it too.

77
00:03:38,700 --> 00:03:40,139
The Zhuang family had a young lady

78
00:03:40,140 --> 00:03:40,979
who spoke French,

79
00:03:40,980 --> 00:03:41,899
played the piano,

80
00:03:41,900 --> 00:03:43,339
and was quite beautiful too.

81
00:03:43,340 --> 00:03:44,100
Commander.

82
00:03:48,260 --> 00:03:50,420
If this lady is lying,

83
00:03:50,540 --> 00:03:51,980
it'll be easy enough to verify.

84
00:03:52,140 --> 00:03:52,979
Besides,

85
00:03:52,980 --> 00:03:54,019
the Zhuang family's

86
00:03:54,020 --> 00:03:55,740
hidden opium stash

87
00:03:56,020 --> 00:03:57,500
was no small matter.

88
00:03:58,580 --> 00:03:59,500
Miss Xue,

89
00:04:00,220 --> 00:04:01,700
don't tell me you're afraid.

90
00:04:07,260 --> 00:04:08,100
Let go.

91
00:04:10,580 --> 00:04:11,740
I'll do it myself.

92
00:04:55,940 --> 00:04:56,580
This...

93
00:04:56,740 --> 00:04:58,140
Why is it a flower?

94
00:05:01,500 --> 00:05:03,020
You must've used it to cover the scar.

95
00:05:03,380 --> 00:05:04,220
Enough!

96
00:05:10,140 --> 00:05:11,060
Commander,

97
00:05:11,660 --> 00:05:12,620
she did it on purpose.

98
00:05:12,980 --> 00:05:14,060
If there isn't a scar,

99
00:05:14,100 --> 00:05:15,580
why would she get a tattoo there?

100
00:05:15,620 --> 00:05:16,299
Because...

101
00:05:16,300 --> 00:05:17,940
Of course it was something I personally

102
00:05:17,980 --> 00:05:19,500
tattooed on my wife
on our wedding night.

103
00:05:19,980 --> 00:05:20,820
Commander,

104
00:05:21,860 --> 00:05:22,980
you...

105
00:05:23,740 --> 00:05:24,940
How is that possible?

106
00:05:25,260 --> 00:05:26,059
Weren't you...

107
00:05:26,060 --> 00:05:26,740
What?

108
00:05:27,300 --> 00:05:29,960
Do you plan on interfering with
what happens between me and my wife too?

109
00:05:30,820 --> 00:05:31,810
I...

110
00:05:31,900 --> 00:05:33,059
Darling. Let's go.

111
00:05:33,060 --> 00:05:36,109
♪Your silhouette♪

112
00:05:36,110 --> 00:05:38,590
♪Carved through endless hardship♪

113
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:44,799
♪Love and longing
traced through countless lifetimes♪

114
00:05:45,880 --> 00:05:51,760
♪Fates intertwined,
right and wrong no longer clear♪

115
00:05:52,740 --> 00:05:53,500
Tell me.

116
00:05:54,420 --> 00:05:56,140
What's the story behind that tattoo?

117
00:05:59,020 --> 00:06:00,580
Didn't you already say it yourself?

118
00:06:00,860 --> 00:06:02,539
A little memory from our wedding night.

119
00:06:02,540 --> 00:06:03,780
Speak properly.

120
00:06:04,930 --> 00:06:06,579
♪Crossing through
the barriers of dreams♪

121
00:06:06,580 --> 00:06:07,999
♪Burning away all my devotion♪

122
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:09,630
Thank you for helping me out just now.

123
00:06:10,980 --> 00:06:13,060
But why did you help me?

124
00:06:14,590 --> 00:06:16,939
♪How can one stay calm in love?♪

125
00:06:16,940 --> 00:06:18,920
Why do you know that song?

126
00:06:19,380 --> 00:06:21,059
♪Nothing more than an excuse♪

127
00:06:21,060 --> 00:06:22,620
Commander, you're hurting me.

128
00:06:23,380 --> 00:06:24,189
Talk.

129
00:06:24,190 --> 00:06:26,719
♪Even if time has given up on us♪

130
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:27,659
That song?

131
00:06:27,660 --> 00:06:30,099
♪I still long to hold you once again♪

132
00:06:30,100 --> 00:06:31,980
Zhuang Yunqiu taught it to me.

133
00:06:32,150 --> 00:06:34,630
What exactly was your relationship
with Zhuang Yunqiu?

134
00:06:36,220 --> 00:06:37,459
Before I went abroad,

135
00:06:37,460 --> 00:06:38,860
we used to be childhood friends.

136
00:06:40,620 --> 00:06:41,660
We were quite close.

137
00:06:46,700 --> 00:06:47,620
So,

138
00:06:49,180 --> 00:06:50,340
you married me

139
00:06:50,580 --> 00:06:52,540
and kept pulling knives on me

140
00:06:54,020 --> 00:06:56,080
because you wanted revenge
for your dear friend?

141
00:06:56,080 --> 00:06:58,410
♪Fates intertwined♪

142
00:06:58,940 --> 00:07:00,500
You're only half right.

143
00:07:01,530 --> 00:07:02,839
♪The world becomes a prison♪

144
00:07:02,840 --> 00:07:07,250
♪Even fleeting happiness is enough♪

145
00:07:07,930 --> 00:07:09,879
♪This heart and love fade away♪

146
00:07:09,880 --> 00:07:11,939
Zhuang Yunqiu and I
were childhood friends,

147
00:07:11,940 --> 00:07:13,860
but we haven't been in contact
for a very long time.

148
00:07:14,500 --> 00:07:16,140
At first,

149
00:07:16,980 --> 00:07:19,300
I truly didn't want to marry a stranger.

150
00:07:19,900 --> 00:07:22,220
But after spending time with you,

151
00:07:22,620 --> 00:07:23,740
I realized

152
00:07:23,900 --> 00:07:26,020
you're even more charming
than I imagined.

153
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:28,850
♪So called blame♪

154
00:07:29,020 --> 00:07:30,420
So the two of you seemed alike

155
00:07:31,620 --> 00:07:33,020
only because you knew each other?

156
00:07:33,580 --> 00:07:35,740
The reason you dislike me
is because of her?

157
00:07:37,420 --> 00:07:38,900
When it comes to Zhuang Yunqiu,

158
00:07:39,380 --> 00:07:40,580
do you feel hatred,

159
00:07:41,140 --> 00:07:42,260
love,

160
00:07:43,820 --> 00:07:45,340
or guilt?

161
00:07:46,320 --> 00:07:49,510
♪If the years are wasted for too long♪

162
00:07:49,540 --> 00:07:52,240
♪How can one stay calm in love?♪

163
00:07:52,740 --> 00:07:55,949
♪So called blame
is nothing but an excuse♪

164
00:07:55,950 --> 00:07:59,129
♪Where in time did my heart belong?♪

165
00:07:59,130 --> 00:08:02,339
♪Even if time has given up on us♪

166
00:08:02,340 --> 00:08:05,489
♪I still long to hold you once again♪

167
00:08:05,490 --> 00:08:08,679
♪When love runs deep,
why fear growing old together?♪

168
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:12,470
♪Let the frost wither
the greenery beyond the window♪

169
00:08:16,460 --> 00:08:17,620
Are they back yet?

170
00:08:18,220 --> 00:08:20,340
Not yet.

171
00:08:24,740 --> 00:08:26,860
That Lu Shaoyuan...

172
00:08:28,140 --> 00:08:30,940
Where exactly did he take my woman?

173
00:08:35,300 --> 00:08:36,700
Go find them now.

174
00:08:36,900 --> 00:08:37,820
Yes, sir.

175
00:09:53,900 --> 00:09:55,100
Lu Shaoyuan!

176
00:10:01,660 --> 00:10:02,340
Darling,

177
00:10:02,540 --> 00:10:03,820
I'm Gu Nianchi.

178
00:10:04,460 --> 00:10:05,580
I'm your husband.

179
00:10:05,940 --> 00:10:06,740
What?

180
00:10:08,180 --> 00:10:09,540
Did you forget, Brother?

181
00:10:10,020 --> 00:10:12,740
You're the one
who begged me to be your stand in.

182
00:10:13,900 --> 00:10:15,019
Lu Shaoyuan,

183
00:10:15,020 --> 00:10:16,620
I'm the one who married her!

184
00:10:18,100 --> 00:10:19,020
Really?

185
00:10:20,020 --> 00:10:24,380
But the one who spent
the wedding night with her was me.

186
00:10:25,860 --> 00:10:27,100
What exactly is going on?

187
00:10:44,420 --> 00:10:45,900
Get out of my sight!

188
00:10:54,900 --> 00:10:56,060
Lieutenant Li!

189
00:10:57,620 --> 00:10:58,420
Commander.

190
00:10:59,580 --> 00:11:00,580
Are they back?

191
00:11:01,380 --> 00:11:02,660
He's already asleep in the study.

192
00:11:03,300 --> 00:11:04,220
What about Madam?

193
00:11:04,660 --> 00:11:05,660
She's back in the bedroom.

194
00:11:08,580 --> 00:11:09,940
(Lu Shaoyuan,)

195
00:11:10,300 --> 00:11:12,060
(you'd better know your place.)

196
00:11:12,900 --> 00:11:15,180
(She belongs to me.)

197
00:11:31,580 --> 00:11:33,820
You really enjoy
doing these pointless things.

198
00:11:35,420 --> 00:11:36,940
I like flowers.

199
00:11:37,380 --> 00:11:39,540
Because I think they're just like love.

200
00:11:39,700 --> 00:11:41,500
When they bloom,
they're dazzling and beautiful.

201
00:11:42,820 --> 00:11:44,320
But nothing in this world lasts forever.

202
00:11:44,980 --> 00:11:46,380
They wither so quickly,

203
00:11:46,980 --> 00:11:48,820
just like love fading away.

204
00:11:52,460 --> 00:11:54,460
Didn't you say before
that you had someone you loved?

205
00:11:55,060 --> 00:11:57,300
Are these feelings because of him?

206
00:12:00,340 --> 00:12:01,260
Commander.

207
00:12:01,740 --> 00:12:02,580
Madam.

208
00:12:05,860 --> 00:12:07,259
I offended you both yesterday.

209
00:12:07,260 --> 00:12:09,500
So today, I'd like to treat you
to a meal as an apology.

210
00:12:11,540 --> 00:12:12,420
I'm not hungry.

211
00:12:13,820 --> 00:12:14,900
I am.

212
00:12:16,940 --> 00:12:18,340
Won't you eat with me?

213
00:12:19,060 --> 00:12:20,100
No.

214
00:12:20,740 --> 00:12:23,860
This is braised fish from Guangde Restaurant,
the most famous restaurant in Yancheng.

215
00:12:23,940 --> 00:12:26,180
I specially ordered it for you.

216
00:12:26,620 --> 00:12:27,740
Madam, give it a try.

217
00:12:31,740 --> 00:12:33,300
You should eat it yourselves.

218
00:12:33,340 --> 00:12:34,379
What a coincidence.

219
00:12:34,380 --> 00:12:35,620
I don't eat fish.

220
00:12:35,780 --> 00:12:37,579
Do you not eat fish,

221
00:12:37,580 --> 00:12:38,860
or do you not dare to eat it?

222
00:12:40,060 --> 00:12:41,460
There are too many bones.

223
00:12:41,580 --> 00:12:43,060
I don't like trouble.

224
00:12:43,360 --> 00:12:48,580
♪Love quietly hides within the wind♪

225
00:12:49,310 --> 00:12:54,219
♪Falling into your smile before my eyes♪

226
00:12:54,220 --> 00:12:55,140
The fish is ready.

227
00:12:56,100 --> 00:12:58,019
Sorry, I can't eat fish.

228
00:12:58,020 --> 00:12:59,059
I'm allergic to it.

229
00:12:59,060 --> 00:13:00,460
I'll break out in red rashes.

230
00:13:03,420 --> 00:13:04,580
Then wait a little longer.

231
00:13:04,660 --> 00:13:06,160
The chicken will be ready soon too.

232
00:13:06,580 --> 00:13:07,500
Chicken is fine.

233
00:13:10,180 --> 00:13:10,939
It's alright.

234
00:13:10,940 --> 00:13:12,540
I can remove the bones for you.

235
00:13:16,060 --> 00:13:17,340
I don't want fish.

236
00:13:18,060 --> 00:13:18,900
Take it away.

237
00:13:19,620 --> 00:13:20,500
Commander,

238
00:13:20,700 --> 00:13:23,380
don't you usually love fish the most?

239
00:13:24,060 --> 00:13:26,580
Then we shouldn't waste Lily's kindness.

240
00:13:26,860 --> 00:13:27,660
You...

241
00:13:28,140 --> 00:13:29,540
You're really going to eat it?

242
00:13:29,940 --> 00:13:31,700
If you don't want to eat,

243
00:13:32,940 --> 00:13:34,340
you don't have to.

244
00:13:35,620 --> 00:13:36,299
Actually,

245
00:13:36,300 --> 00:13:37,860
I do quite like fish.

246
00:13:38,140 --> 00:13:39,780
I just don't like removing the bones.

247
00:13:40,100 --> 00:13:43,260
Especially when a stranger
does it for me.

248
00:13:45,940 --> 00:13:46,780
Commander,

249
00:13:47,420 --> 00:13:48,419
can you help me?

250
00:13:48,420 --> 00:13:51,970
♪In this world♪

251
00:13:56,710 --> 00:14:01,400
♪How can broken love ever go on?♪

252
00:14:02,710 --> 00:14:08,030
♪How much hope must fade into despair?♪

253
00:14:08,530 --> 00:14:12,110
♪In the blink of an eye,
everything falls apart♪

254
00:14:12,450 --> 00:14:15,460
♪Bound by the fate we cannot escape♪

255
00:14:15,630 --> 00:14:20,750
♪You and I caught in
this tangled love and hate♪

256
00:14:21,870 --> 00:14:27,060
♪Fragile hearts can hardly bear goodbye♪

257
00:14:28,120 --> 00:14:33,720
♪How many times
must pain cut deep before we wake?♪

258
00:14:34,260 --> 00:14:37,640
♪I once gave myself
to you so completely♪

259
00:14:37,890 --> 00:14:40,839
♪Still holding on to that heart♪

260
00:14:40,840 --> 00:14:45,979
♪Only to suffer your fatal blow♪

261
00:14:45,980 --> 00:14:50,299
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

262
00:14:50,300 --> 00:14:52,879
♪Yet I approach you with such caution♪

263
00:14:52,880 --> 00:14:55,159
♪How could a stand in ever have♪

264
00:14:55,160 --> 00:14:58,709
♪The right to be loved by you?♪

265
00:14:58,710 --> 00:15:03,239
♪If love is nothing
more than endless schemes♪

266
00:15:03,240 --> 00:15:05,770
♪Used and abandoned in the end♪

267
00:15:05,910 --> 00:15:07,859
♪Still I walk into♪

268
00:15:07,860 --> 00:15:11,459
♪The trap you set without regret♪

269
00:15:11,460 --> 00:15:15,509
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

270
00:15:15,510 --> 00:15:18,089
♪Yet keep it buried deep inside♪

271
00:15:18,090 --> 00:15:20,249
♪A stand in can never cross♪

272
00:15:20,250 --> 00:15:23,689
♪The shortest distance between us♪

273
00:15:23,690 --> 00:15:28,660
♪If love can
make someone lose themselves♪

274
00:15:28,820 --> 00:15:33,490
♪Then let me stay by your side♪

275
00:15:36,270 --> 00:15:37,839
♪A substitute♪

276
00:15:37,840 --> 00:15:42,840
♪Needs no reason♪

